Build a React + D3.js + Three.js AI Documentary Map Animation Engine.

Goal:
Create a web application that generates YouTube-style animated geography/data visualization videos.

Tech stack:
- React + Vite
- D3.js for 2D maps and data visualization
- Three.js + React Three Fiber for 3D rotating globe
- TopoJSON / GeoJSON for country boundaries
- FFmpeg/WebCodecs for video export

